#. type: Content of: <guide><abstract>
#: en/bluetooth-guide.xml:28
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This guide will explain how to successfully install a host Bluetooth device,\n"
"configure the kernel properly, explain all the possibilities that the Bluetooth\n"
"interconnection offers and how to have some fun with Bluetooth.\n"
msgstr ""
"このガイドには、Bluetoothデバイスをホストに導入しカーネルを正しく構成する手順が書かれています。\n"
"さらに、Blutooth技術にできることやBlutoothの使い方も紹介します。\n"

